{
  "stem": "15578.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was in the what it called the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My brother, he got married, and he moved the shop to his place.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] 5.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would say so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My brother.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nojech.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, very much so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sometime.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] [SIGHS] What can I say?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Just unfortunately.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] [SIGHS] [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] I can't say anything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Paula.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Elbaum.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 17 SECONDS] [SIGHS]",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We did.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We knew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And nobody could believe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't know very much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The only thing I remember, we were-- were in a play at that time, and they said that Hitler-- 1933 when [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Kaiser Wilhelm or whatever it was, that he became Chancellor, that's all.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Something like this.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the rest, nobody did believe that something like this could ever happen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What he'd done to the Jewish population.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1933, because in that time, not right in 1933, a few years later, he's sent out Jewish people from Germany.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they did come from Poland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So a lot of people did come to Poland from Germany-- Jewish people at that time-- 1937, '38.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a family that come over.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Their name was Markowic.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And he was in Germany before the war, and he married to a German woman.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there-- and they have two children, a daughter and a son.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The son's name was Julius.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I think in 1937 or in '38, they was-- they sent him out-- they had family in Tomaszow.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they did come.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then his wife-- she was German, real German-- and she did come to Tomaszow too.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She didn't want to leave them alone.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
